<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SLTV – Use Our Official Mobile App</title>
    <meta name="description" content="For the best viewing experience, please use our official SLTV Mobile App. Stream Sri Lankan TV channels live in HD.">
    
    <!-- Open Graph -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="SLTV – Use Our Official Mobile App">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Get the best experience on our mobile app. Watch Hiru TV, Derana, ITN, and more.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="../images/Og.jpg">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://sltvapp.techlasiya.com/livetv/">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff3d00;
            --secondary: #ff9100;
            --bg: #0a0a0a;
            --text: #ffffff;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
        }

        /* Animated Background */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, var(--primary) 0%, transparent 40%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 70%, var(--secondary) 0%, transparent 40%);
            opacity: 0.12;
            filter: blur(80px);
            animation: move 25s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        @keyframes move {
            from { transform: translate(-5%, -5%) rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: translate(5%, 5%) rotate(10deg); }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px) saturate(180%);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px) saturate(180%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            animation: containerAppear 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        @keyframes containerAppear {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9) translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
        }

        .logo {
            width: 100px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(255, 61, 0, 0.4));
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .og-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #a0a0a0 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(255, 61, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(255, 61, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(0.98);
        }

        .btn svg {
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            stroke-width: 2.5;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 35px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Mobile Specific Refinement */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 35px 20px;
                border-radius: 32px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .logo {
                width: 80px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .og-image {
                border-radius: 18px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .btn {
                padding: 16px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
                border-radius: 18px;
            }
        }

        /* Handle very small heights */
        @media (max-height: 650px) {
            body {
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 30px;
                padding-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .container {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .og-image {
                display: none; /* Hide image on very small viewports to prioritize text/button */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nxt-owner/SLTV-APP/refs/heads/main/images/logo/logo.png" alt="SLTV Logo" class="logo">
        
        <img src="../images/Og.jpg" alt="App Preview" class="og-image">

        <h1>Please Use Our Official Mobile App</h1>
        <p>For the best live streaming experience with lower latency and exclusive features, please download and use our official mobile application.</p>

        <a href="https://sltvapp.techlasiya.com/" class="btn">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
                <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline>
                <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
            </svg>
            Download Official App
        </a>

        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 SLTV. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>